High Level Goals.
  1. User should be able to select the PDF(book) he wants to read.
  2. User should be able to pause/ start the audio.
  3. User should be able to skip to a specific page in the PDF(book).
  4. The application should run standalone , an executable file should be there
     which will start the application , the script should not start manually.
  5. A nice GUI for better user experience.
